 
<p>

Zelensky explains why a temporary cease-fire would <a href="https://archive.ph/Mk5Lm">help the Putin
forces</a> in the long term.
<p>
We must not allow Putin to succeed in <a href="https://stallman.org/archives/2022-mar-jun.html#8_June_2022_(Russia_succeeding_in_holding_out_against_sanctions)">capturing and holding Ukrainian
territory</a>, but as long as we prevent that, it makes sense to help him <a href="https://stallman.org/archives/2022-mar-jun.html#7_June_2022_(Emmanuel_Macron:_Russia_must_not_be_humiliated_in_Ukraine)">save face</a>.

 